# Day 19 – CloudWatch Logs & Troubleshooting

## Goal
Learn how to use CloudWatch Logs to identify and fix issues.

## Steps
- Enabled CloudWatch Agent on EC2.
- Sent system/application logs to CloudWatch.
- Viewed logs in CloudWatch console.
- Searched for errors using filters.
- Troubleshot app crash by reading error messages.
- Created metric filter + alarm for error monitoring.

## Lessons Learned
- Logs show the real cause of issues.
- Filtering helps find problems fast.
- Alarms notify you before customers complain.

